' Modelo final del Observatorio Económico y de Mercados de Bolivia
' Fuente: elaboración propia basada en SDMX 3.1, GSIM 2.0, UN-NQAF e INE Bolivia.
' Archivo autónomo: no requiere includes externos.

@startuml
title Estado — data_entry_batch
skinparam shadowing false
[*] --> CREATED
CREATED --> VALIDATING : start
CREATED --> CANCELLED : cancel
VALIDATING --> REJECTED : invalidSchema / criticalError
VALIDATING --> ACCEPTED : structuralValidationPassed
ACCEPTED --> COMMITTING : persist
COMMITTING --> COMMITTED : allAccepted
COMMITTING --> PARTIAL : someRejected
COMMITTING --> FAILED : transactionOrInfrastructureFailure
FAILED --> VALIDATING : authorizedRetry
REJECTED --> [*]
COMMITTED --> [*]
PARTIAL --> [*]
CANCELLED --> [*]

note right of PARTIAL
Los registros aceptados y rechazados
quedan contabilizados y trazables.
end note
@enduml
